lead_paragraph: Josh Donaldson hit two home runs and drove in five runs as the Toronto Blue Jays snapped a five-game home losing streak with a 7-5 win over the Boston Red Sox on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Donaldson Powers Blue Jays Past Red Sox 7-5
